{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088400/extras/waglewagledt.png?t=1735275166\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>'Deadly Trick' is a anime style social deduction survival game!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Supply power to the bomb collar to prevent it from exploding.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The goal of the game is to survive the 'special class', a death game taking place at Lastope School.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088400/extras/\uc900\ube44.gif?t=1735275166\" /><strong>Gather your friends and play together!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088400/extras/\ud3ec\uc778\ud2b8_\uc6b4\uc601.gif?t=1735275166\" /><strong>You can earn bonus points during the game. Bonus points can be used in a variety of ways!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>For example, you can recharge your batteries to survive, or buy a weapon to turn black.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088400/extras/3.jpg?t=1735275166\" /><strong>In 'Deadly Trick', there are no roles assigned from the start of the game!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Depending on your choice, anyone can become either a kind white or a cruel black!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>What drives that choice are the various \u2018situations\u2019 that occur between players...!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_para